Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.13,0:00:02.99,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}As bright as a spark,\Nwith a sharp and precise wit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.99,0:00:04.77,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Once he gets started,\Nyou can't stop him!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.77,0:00:07.07,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Today, there's lots of Sonoko\Nin her natural state.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.07,0:00:08.90,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Danger, romance and fate await!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.90,0:00:10.64,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He sees the single truth\Nfor what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.64,0:00:12.48,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and looks like a kid\Nbut has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.48,0:00:15.07,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name?\NDetective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.47,0:02:02.08,Signs,,0,0,0,,Izu
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.99,0:02:13.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.30,0:02:16.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Sonoko! What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.69,0:02:20.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Taking a picture of your butt while\Nyou were fixing your swimsuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.64,0:02:22.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A real close-up!\NIt's an eyeful!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.66,0:02:25.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do\Nwith a photo like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.36,0:02:27.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.02,0:02:29.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna show it to Shin'ichi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}\Nwhen he gets back!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.54,0:02:33.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Think how happy he'll be!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.75,0:02:35.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't be silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.28,0:02:38.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shin'ichi wouldn't be\Nhappy about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.34,0:02:41.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you think\Nso too, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.23,0:02:43.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Umm, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.74,0:02:46.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What does a little kid know?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.64,0:02:49.98,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Ugh... I can't {\i1}wait{\i0} to\Nget back to normal...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.98,0:02:52.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've been acting weird, Sonoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.43,0:02:54.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've been picking on me\Nnon-stop for a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.79,0:02:58.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't mind me.\NI'm just a bit jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.15,0:03:01.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? Why?\NDid I do something?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.71,0:03:03.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haven't you noticed, Ran?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.51,0:03:07.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why'd we come on a weekend\Nbeach trip to Izu in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.70,0:03:10.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For you, it's your usual\Nman-hunting trip, isn't it, Sonoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.79,0:03:12.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.00,0:03:16.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And it's a carefully planned\Npoor girl vacation, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.17,0:03:19.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you on about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.46,0:03:25.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We always stay at my family's\Nsummer house, or an expensive hotel!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.35,0:03:29.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Oh, {\i1}how{\i0} can I talk to a girl\Nwho's so far beyond my reach?"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.85,0:03:34.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This time, we're staying at an old inn,\Nwhere we can reel in unexpecting boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.77,0:03:37.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.68,0:03:38.98,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.98,0:03:43.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But... But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.53,0:03:44.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.91,0:03:47.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the train here...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.87,0:03:52.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At the fireworks show last night...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.62,0:03:54.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And even at this beach...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.92,0:04:00.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All of the guys are after you.\NEvery single one of them, Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.91,0:04:03.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.58,0:04:06.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.26,0:04:10.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll just show Shin'ichi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} a photo of you\Nin your underwear that I took last night!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.58,0:04:12.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.13,0:04:14.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't even think about it, Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.87,0:04:16.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you do that,\NI'll never forgive you for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.64,0:04:23.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just kidding.\NNever took any photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.15,0:04:25.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For crying out loud, Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.57,0:04:27.70,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh, she was bluffing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.19,0:04:29.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you two...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.89,0:04:31.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you busy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.25,0:04:35.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would you like to get some lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.93,0:04:36.60,Signs,,0,0,0,,Tadahiko Michiwaki
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.07,0:04:36.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's on me, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.58,0:04:39.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes! We'd love...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.46,0:04:40.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.56,0:04:43.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You want {\i1}her{\i0}, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.99,0:04:46.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here, take her! She's in season!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.30,0:04:48.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.53,0:04:51.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But don't try anything funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.15,0:04:53.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's already taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.67,0:04:58.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Er, I was kinda hoping to\Nget to know {\i1}you{\i0} better.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.61,0:04:59.98,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.98,0:05:02.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You did it, Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.08,0:05:02.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.84,0:05:07.49,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Impossible. This is Sonoko\Nwe're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.36,0:05:14.30,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There has to be\Nsomething behind this...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.67,0:05:18.83,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I've {\i1}got{\i0} to stop thinking\Nlike a detective all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.71,0:05:20.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.50,0:05:24.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} and I\Nwill stay here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.64,0:05:36.39,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,{\c&H905C73&\3c&HBBC2C3&}Nagisa {\c&H57515C&}Beach House\N{\c&H403F4D&}Famous for our {\c&H4F4484&}Grilled Amberjack
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.53,0:05:40.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're a student at Beika\NUniversity, Michiwaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.11,0:05:43.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran's dad used to\Nstudy there, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.42,0:05:44.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.08,0:05:46.44,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.44,0:05:50.53,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}She gets all excited about a guy,\Nbut she wimps out and drags us along?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.96,0:05:55.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, Michiwaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r},\Nwhat brings you to Izu?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.03,0:05:56.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just a trip\Nto heal a broken heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.55,0:05:59.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My girlfriend dumped me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.32,0:06:03.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was gazing into\Nthe sea in despair...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.41,0:06:07.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...when an angel\Nappeared before me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.09,0:06:14.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have a hunch you're the\Ngoddess who's going to save me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.45,0:06:18.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,G-Goddess?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.58,0:06:24.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here's your draft beer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.24,0:06:25.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.42,0:06:33.47,Signs,,0,0,0,,Makoto Kyogoku
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.94,0:06:31.68,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Sir, please don't drop cigarette\Nbutts all over the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.68,0:06:33.45,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,They're a pain to clean up later.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.96,0:06:35.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,R-Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.13,0:06:40.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a rude waiter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.14,0:06:41.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.88,0:06:44.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haven't we seen that\Nwaiter somewhere before?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.58,0:06:49.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course we have. His dad owns\Nthe inn where we're staying!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.43,0:06:53.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's come to help\Nover summer vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.67,0:06:55.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.90,0:07:00.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was staring at us from the front steps\Nof the inn, so I asked one of the workers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.30,0:07:04.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then why's he working {\i1}here{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.67,0:07:09.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's probably run by the same person who takes\Ncare of Kawaraya Inn, where we're staying.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.40,0:07:13.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh? You're staying at Kawaraya Inn?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.22,0:07:15.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.04,0:07:18.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fancy that, it's right next to my hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.86,0:07:23.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then how about we all have dinner at\Na fancy restaurant by the sea tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.72,0:07:25.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll pick you up in my car.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.04,0:07:27.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.69,0:07:29.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But don't forget to\Nbring your camera!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.66,0:07:31.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.18,0:07:34.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just learned this from a local,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.54,0:07:37.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but there was an incident at\Nthe beach near the restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.89,0:07:39.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An incident?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.88,0:07:41.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.07,0:07:42.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About a year ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.63,0:07:49.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,a girl with long brown hair was stabbed\Nrepeatedly in the stomach and killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.59,0:07:50.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A murder?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.09,0:07:52.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.11,0:07:57.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was killed on her\Nway to that restaurant,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.00,0:07:59.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but there were no witnesses.\NThe police are still looking for the killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.03,0:08:01.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's been a year since the case,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.84,0:08:06.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so most people forgot about it,\Nand the restaurant's doing well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.94,0:08:14.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, she seems to have taken a\Nliking to that restaurant, and still drops by...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.55,0:08:15.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Still...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.43,0:08:18.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The victimized woman shows up...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.71,0:08:23.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,as a grotesque ghost in photos taken inside the restaurant!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.01,0:08:27.44,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's just stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.98,0:08:32.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So let's see if she really\Nappears in a photograph.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.46,0:08:35.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.28,0:08:37.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I still have about ten\Nshots left in my camera...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.33,0:08:40.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No! Don't even bring it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.64,0:08:44.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if we showed it to Shin'ichi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r},\Nhe might notice something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.92,0:08:49.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, we're going to show him\Nthe {\i1}shocking{\i0} photo, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.71,0:08:53.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the point of showing him that one?\NYou can't even tell who it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.61,0:08:59.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He could figure it out with\Nhis super deductive skills!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.45,0:09:00.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.59,0:09:01.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Deductive skills?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.21,0:09:04.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her boyfriend's a detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.61,0:09:05.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, he is?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.65,0:09:09.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And what's in that photo?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.16,0:09:10.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.02,0:09:10.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.46,0:09:13.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here's your yakisoba.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.82,0:09:17.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've got a lot of customers waiting,\Nso hurry up and eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.77,0:09:25.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, what's with that waiter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.32,0:09:27.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Does he have a grudge\Nagainst us or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.69,0:09:30.69,Signs,,0,0,0,,Shoji Terabayashi
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.22,0:09:34.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can't we eat somewhere\Nother than that restaurant?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.21,0:09:35.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It sounds creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.10,0:09:37.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.84,0:09:42.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The ghost thing's just a rumor,\Nand it's been a year since the murder!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.53,0:09:46.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure the dead woman got\Nbored of that restaurant by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.58,0:09:48.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, did you hear?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.81,0:09:52.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They found another one in\Nthe forest by the train tracks!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.39,0:09:53.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Another what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.02,0:09:54.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A body!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.81,0:09:57.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The bloody body of a\Nwoman with brown hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.95,0:10:01.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll be right back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.23,0:10:02.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.09,0:10:05.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.18,0:10:11.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sheesh, what a bundle of curiosity.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.49,0:10:28.21,Signs,,0,0,0,,Detective Yokomizo\NShizuoka Police Detective
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.10,0:10:26.35,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Stabbed multiple times\Nin the abdominal area.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.35,0:10:28.18,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Just like a year ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.70,0:10:29.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.75,0:10:32.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This woman seems to\Nhave been a tourist, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.32,0:10:34.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, what's the\Nestimated time of death?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.36,0:10:38.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Between 8 and 9 PM last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.83,0:10:41.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So it was right after the fireworks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.46,0:10:47.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, isn't that around\Nthe time we passed by here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.00,0:10:48.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.78,0:10:51.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.36,0:10:52.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't be silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.38,0:10:54.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no way you'll be attacked!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.72,0:10:57.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But look at me!\NI have brown hair too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.46,0:11:00.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no guarantee\NI won't be next!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.95,0:11:05.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't want to die out here...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.98,0:11:10.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not with my whole\Nlife ahead of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.06,0:11:13.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.00,0:11:17.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.11,0:11:19.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll protect you as long\Nas you're here in Izu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.64,0:11:24.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I guess we should{\rHonorifics - Dialogue} chan{\r}ge\Nour dinner reservations, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.44,0:11:24.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.86,0:11:27.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A-And no cameras!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.42,0:11:28.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.25,0:11:31.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll pick you up around 7.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.11,0:11:32.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait for me in front of the inn!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.95,0:11:34.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.28,0:11:41.05,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Wasn't that guy just at\Nthe Beach House, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.37,0:11:43.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See you then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.10,0:11:45.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NI'll be looking forward to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.02,0:11:53.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We should go back\Nto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue} chan{\r}ge clothes, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.07,0:11:53.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.64,0:11:55.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.73,0:11:58.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it isn't Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.46,0:11:59.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you've come to Izu, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.14,0:12:01.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we came for the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.98,0:12:04.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, is the great\NDetective Mouri here too?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.74,0:12:07.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it's just us three.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.02,0:12:09.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Three?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.09,0:12:10.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good afternoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.87,0:12:15.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, you're the knight accompanying\Nthese two damsels, huh, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.03,0:12:16.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Be sure to protect them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.29,0:12:18.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.09,0:12:21.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.08,0:12:23.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As you can see,\Nwe've had a troubling incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.83,0:12:25.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. We'll be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.83,0:12:27.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then I'll be leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.83,0:12:31.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Give Detective Mouri my regards.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.25,0:12:32.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.47,0:12:39.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's as cheerful\Nas always, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.58,0:12:41.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like he's not\Nhaving any luck, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.20,0:12:45.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If your dad was here,\Nhe'd solve the case in no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.60,0:12:53.35,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10\fad(0,1725)}Detective Yokomizo is {\i1}far{\i0} more\Ncompetent than the old man...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.27,0:13:10.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's starting to rain...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.59,0:13:14.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hope Michiwaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}\Nshows up soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.87,0:13:16.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.87,0:13:19.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The hero always appears\Nat the last second!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.23,0:13:22.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop! You're embarrassing me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.59,0:13:30.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's with the umbrella?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.51,0:13:31.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess he wants us to use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.51,0:13:36.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe he's got a crush\Non you, Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.16,0:13:40.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're getting popular, Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.74,0:13:42.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not the dark guy too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.48,0:13:46.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, you already\Nhave Michiwaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.00,0:13:50.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop it, Ran,\Nyou're making me blush...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.02,0:13:52.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, drat.\NI left my purse in my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.42,0:13:55.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on,\NI'll be back in a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.58,0:13:56.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.46,0:14:07.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.07,0:14:13.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I {\i1}know{\i0} I've seen the guy\Nin glasses somewhere, but where?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.46,0:14:15.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Somewhere in this inn, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.32,0:14:18.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, not just here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.87,0:14:20.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Somewhere else...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.57,0:14:31.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.19,0:14:43.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where? Where'd you\Nsee him, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.22,0:14:45.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.13,0:15:08.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko? What's taking you so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.62,0:15:14.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe she's{\rHonorifics - Dialogue} chan{\r}ging...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.64,0:15:19.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko! What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.67,0:15:23.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A weird guy jumped me...\NHe escaped through the window...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.77,0:15:25.15,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.26,0:15:30.90,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Damn! He got away...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.58,0:15:33.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was so scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.56,0:15:35.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why would anybody...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.47,0:15:36.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How should I know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.49,0:15:41.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I opened the door,\Nhe was searching our bags.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.74,0:15:44.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I tried to shout,\Nand he grabbed me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.72,0:15:46.38,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Searching our bags?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.77,0:15:49.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I bet he was trying to\Nsteal our underwear! Yuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.29,0:15:52.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What did he look like?\NYou saw his face, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.30,0:15:55.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I never had the{\rHonorifics - Dialogue} chan{\r}ce...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.03,0:15:56.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was pitch dark in here...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.62,0:15:58.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was so scared,\NI just about passed out...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.39,0:16:01.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But how do you know it's a guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.93,0:16:06.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I bit his arm in the struggle.\NIt was hairy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.91,0:16:09.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Way to go...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.33,0:16:12.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.40,0:16:14.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are the lights out?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.32,0:16:15.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Michiwaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.23,0:16:20.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My car broke down on the way here,\Nso I ran here as fast as I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.71,0:16:22.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please accept my\Napologies for being late.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.00,0:16:23.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But how'd you find our room?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.68,0:16:28.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't find you two outside,\Nso I asked one of the staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.94,0:16:33.91,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His shirt's wet\Nand his pants are muddy...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.91,0:16:34.80,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Don't tell me, he...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.51,0:16:37.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Michiwaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.10,0:16:38.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would you mind\Ntaking your shirt off?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.84,0:16:42.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was wondering if you could\Nshow me your upper arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.16,0:16:43.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.14,0:16:45.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure what you mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.92,0:16:47.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is there anything\Nwrong with my arm?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.61,0:16:52.24,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Nothing. No tooth\Nmarks from Sonoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.72,0:16:54.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Happy now, kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.38,0:16:55.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.59,0:16:59.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is anything wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.14,0:17:03.25,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A bandage!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.07,0:17:06.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What happened to your right arm?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.66,0:17:10.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is from a little struggle I had with a drunk customer earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.74,0:17:13.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When was that? Please tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.64,0:17:18.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't think it was him.\NThe guy who attacked me was hairier.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.09,0:17:19.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Attacked?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.35,0:17:24.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. A man came in through this\Nwindow, dug through our bags,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.96,0:17:27.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and attacked Sonoko when she\Nhappened to walk in on him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.32,0:17:32.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he ran off as soon\Nas he heard us coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.99,0:17:35.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Must've been a thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.86,0:17:37.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've had this happen before.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.57,0:17:40.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You did? Then why\Ndidn't you tell us?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.48,0:17:46.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I {\i1}did{\i0} tell you to make\Nsure to lock up, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.75,0:17:54.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Walking around in a midriff top at this\Ntime of night, what are you expecting?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.86,0:17:59.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're practically {\i1}asking{\i0}\Nto be attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.22,0:18:02.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It doesn't even look\Ngood on you, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.41,0:18:05.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is my favorite top, you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.89,0:18:09.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. You look\Ngood in anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.42,0:18:11.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yukata, swimsuit, whatever!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.36,0:18:16.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.07,0:18:20.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going to move you.\NThere's another room open.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.80,0:18:26.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unless you want to spend the night\Nin the room where you were attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.97,0:18:27.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.98,0:18:32.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd also advise you not to go out,\Nand have dinner here at the inn instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.59,0:18:36.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You never know if that man\Nmight be waiting for you outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.96,0:18:39.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-What do we do, Ran?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.94,0:18:42.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's eat here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.80,0:18:54.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The food's much better than I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.54,0:18:57.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we'd known this before,\Nwe would've eaten here last night, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.81,0:19:02.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We would've been able to get you a nicer meal\Nif you'd made reservations in advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.61,0:19:06.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, the meal's on the house...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.61,0:19:13.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...if you don't spread any "rumors"\Nabout a thief lurking around the inn.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.98,0:19:17.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, right! Whatever!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.56,0:19:21.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I won't talk about the inn with an\Nunderwear thief who pulled a knife on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.42,0:19:22.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A knife?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.86,0:19:24.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.95,0:19:29.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I caught a glimpse of it shining in the light coming through the side screen!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.69,0:19:31.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was a sharp, gleaming knife!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.33,0:19:33.70,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It couldn't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.70,0:19:39.11,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What if our thief is the same man who\Nkilled the woman found in the woods today?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.03,0:19:46.22,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Supposedly a year ago, here in Izu,\Na brown-haired woman was stabbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.75,0:19:52.49,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But why would the\Nkiller target Sonoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.49,0:19:55.79,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Just because she has brown hair?\NThat's ridiculous...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.42,0:19:57.79,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Hold on...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.79,0:20:02.05,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The guy who attacked Sonoko\Nransacked her belongings.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.97,0:20:07.97,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There's one thing in her luggage that\Ncould be connected to the murders.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.03,0:20:10.37,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The camera!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.37,0:20:14.44,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Maybe one of the photos captured\Nsomething related to the murder!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.90,0:20:18.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}! Did the guy who\Nattacked you steal your camera?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.27,0:20:21.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was still in my bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.10,0:20:22.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the compartment\Nwhere I had it {\i1}was{\i0} open.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.99,0:20:24.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So he stole the film?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.95,0:20:27.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It wasn't there in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.58,0:20:29.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since I finished off\Nall thirty-six photos,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.93,0:20:32.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought we could all\Nlook at them over dinner,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.67,0:20:34.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so I had them developed\Nthis afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.24,0:20:36.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See?\NI've got the photos here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.14,0:20:39.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mind if I take a look?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.00,0:20:40.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.17,0:20:40.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Wai—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.17,0:20:43.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.53,0:20:46.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I kept that special photo\Nof you for safe-keeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.12,0:20:49.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't scare me like that, Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.59,0:20:52.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know all of these people?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.50,0:20:54.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You seem to have interrupted\Na lot of lovers...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.49,0:20:58.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko was all cranky\Nbefore she met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.26,0:21:02.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She kept pranking\Nall the couples we met!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.69,0:21:03.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,R-Ran...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.49,0:21:08.25,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Strange... There's nothing\Nodd about the photos.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.25,0:21:10.25,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I don't see the victim, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.54,0:21:17.50,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}We {\i1}did{\i0} pass through the forest\Nwhere the body was found last night,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.50,0:21:20.39,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}but Sonoko didn't\Ntake any photos then.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.98,0:21:28.68,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}So what made the killer think\NSonoko'd taken an incriminating photo?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.54,0:21:32.35,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.56,0:21:38.09,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Maybe someone overheard her at lunch...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.94,0:21:43.57,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He could figure it out with\Nhis super deductive skills!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.57,0:21:47.91,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,{\c&H465EA5&\3c&H649FDA&}Nagisa {\c&H57515C&}Beach House\N{\c&H403F4D&}Famous for our {\c&H3553B7&}Grilled Amberjack
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.31,0:21:47.95,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The killer could've been in\Nthe Beach House at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.80,0:21:51.76,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But was it really {\i1}that{\i0}\Nsuspicious a remark?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.82,0:21:56.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you're going home\Ntomorrow at noon, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.41,0:21:57.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.95,0:22:01.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So how about we stop by the\Ncursed restaurant in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.73,0:22:02.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.97,0:22:04.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It won't be as scary\Nin the daylight!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.20,0:22:07.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But no cameras!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.12,0:22:08.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.90,0:22:16.35,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Am I imagining things,\Nor does this guy keep watching us?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.09,0:22:22.02,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And what about that guy in the glasses,\Nthe one Ran thinks she's seen before?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.76,0:22:25.44,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And as for the guy\Nwho attacked Sonoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.37,0:22:30.54,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Was he really just a simple thief?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.39,0:24:07.88,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The hand brake's disengaged!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.88,0:24:09.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko, wake up! Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.25,0:24:20.64,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's him again!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.53,0:24:25.06,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh no!\NSonoko's in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.06,0:24:31.09,Signs,,0,0,0,,Next Conan:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.06,0:24:51.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint: Toothmarks
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.05,0:24:51.91,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Next time...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.91,0:24:53.42,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Finally Sonoko's got herself a boyfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.42,0:24:54.30,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.30,0:24:56.30,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,This won't end with just being happy!
